        </p>

        <a href="/" style="
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: clamp(13px, 4vw, 14px);
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #000;
        ">
            Go to Home
        </a>

    </div>

